{"tid":2488296,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"重光團隊倫敦登大型實體廣告 　轟中共徹底破壞香港自治籲國際續懲罰","createTime":"2021-04-14T06:49:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T06:49:49.000Z","uid":271829,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a6933c0e5904033bfbc2ad79b04a5d2edf4af078","tid":2488296,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T06:49:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/1Ym0Dlemm0sl1gxcpWXpsOQaxLM=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JIELLJB635CFBNHGXGRDFL2KVA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F1Ym0Dlemm0sl1gxcpWXpsOQaxLM%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJIELLJB635CFBNHGXGRDFL2KVA.png&h=066f80e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5KAL4nZ8gAIQkJBC8mdk3ZCnqFo=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HS6ZIFCVA5EX3LAOB7NJAH7ORQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5KAL4nZ8gAIQkJBC8mdk3ZCnqFo%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHS6ZIFCVA5EX3LAOB7NJAH7ORQ.jpg&h=939ff5b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n廣告刊登在倫敦其中一條最繁忙的公路上，整個活動為期3周。Fight for Freedom. Stand with Hong Kong Facebook圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/zHf5_CTsvLNxssN8AyVR4T1hpCM=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IPJ6JUBBPRCKZE3I3UYJMVUZJI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FzHf5_CTsvLNxssN8AyVR4T1hpCM%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIPJ6JUBBPRCKZE3I3UYJMVUZJI.jpg&h=a0258a09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n廣告內容提到「WE DARE TO BE FREE」（我們敢於自由）。Fight for Freedom. Stand with Hong Kong Facebook圖片<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n「重光團隊」（Stand With Hong Kong）聯同5個在英協助港人的機構，在英國倫敦公路刊登大型實體廣告，內容提到「HONG KONG IS NOT A PLACE, HONG KONG IS ITS PEOPLE」（香港不止是一個地方，香港就是當地民眾）、「WE DARE TO BE FREE」（我們敢於自由）、「LET&rsquo;s FIND STRENGTH IN EACH OTHER」（讓每個人都能找到自己的力量）等。團隊表示，希望藉此推廣香港民族身份及文化，並呼籲國際繼續懲罰中共。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210414/NEUT2EM3JRA6BCKUEON6LGPCHQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210414%2FNEUT2EM3JRA6BCKUEON6LGPCHQ%2F&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1Tvbkzvt9AtAt3lYzSqFOpIRNeugk%3D&h=fb4c8b87\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210414%2FNEUT2EM3JRA6BCKUEON6LGPCHQ%2F&h=381d5cf8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210414/NEUT2EM3JRA6BCKUEON6LGPCHQ/</a>"}]}